            table
                thead
                    tr
                        th Property name
                        th Description
                tbody
                    tr
                        td `id`
                        td Menu unique id 
                    tr
                        td `list`
                        td Array of menu items
                    tr
                        td `text`
                        td Menu item text 
                    tr
                        td `link`
                        td Menu item Url
                    tr
                        td `current`
                        td `true`, `false` value for current active menu item
                    tr
                        td `drawer`
                        td `true`, `false` if true the item will be displayed only on drawer "small screen size"
            p
                b note:
                | The menu could be nested for no limited number of times

